{"type":"message","id":"c2c94c9e","parentId":"eef654ab","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:38:45.557Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，首次提交完成了。现在需要配置远程仓库，让后续的修改、配置、身份、性格、长期记忆、创建技能等操作能自动触发 GitHub 备份。\n\n但是我没有远程仓库的地址。老板可能需要提供，或者我需要询问。\n\n不过，我可以先设置一个 git hook 来实现自动提交和推送。让我创建一个 post-commit hook。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **首次 Git 提交完成！**\n\n现在配置自动触发 GitHub 备份的 hook：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_aa7fdb4d1fe246ed9a6a2b78","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\14015\\.openclaw\\workspace\\.git\\hooks\\post-commit","content":"#!/bin/sh\n# 小虾自动备份钩子 - 提交后自动推送到 GitHub\n# 触发条件：修改配置、身份、性格、长期记忆、创建/安装技能时\n\necho \"🦐 小虾：检测到重要变更，自动触发 GitHub 备份...\"\n\n# 自动推送（如果配置了远程仓库）\ngit remote -v | grep -q origin && git push origin master 2>/dev/null\nif [ $? -eq 0 ]; then\n    echo \"✓ 备份已推送到 GitHub\"\nelse\n    echo \"⚠ 远程仓库未配置，仅本地提交\"\nfi\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":20414,"output":361,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20775,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772419119856}}
