{"type":"message","id":"5391f8d4","parentId":"e46caa8a","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:40:52.901Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to:\n1. Check if there are skills for opening software or clicking (UI automation)\n2. Specifically mentions Midscene.js as one they know about\n3. Wants me to list all the skills I have available\n\nLet me search for skills related to UI automation, and also check my available skills from the system prompt. I should also search the web for Midscene.js to understand what it does.\n\nFrom my system prompt, I can see these available skills:\n- coding-agent\n- healthcheck\n- openai-whisper\n- oracle\n- skill-creator\n- video-frames\n- weather\n\nAnd I have these tools available:\n- browser (browser control)\n- canvas (node canvas control)\n- nodes (device control including camera/screen/notifications)\n- exec (shell commands)\n- process (manage background processes)\n- message (send messages)\n- etc.\n\nLet me search for skills related to UI automation and also check what Midscene.js is.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_524e5847f9cd4a09b6d779d0","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"Midscene.js UI automation Windows","count":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":20802,"output":468,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21270,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772419248498}}
