  \r\nbear-notes         ?     \r\nblogwatcher        ?     \r\nblucli             ?     \r\nbluebubbles        ?     \r\ncamsnap            ?     \r\ncanvas             ?     \r\nclawhub            ?     \r\ncoding-agent       ?     \r\ndiscord            ?     \r\neightctl           ?     \r\ngemini             ?     \r\ngh-issues          ?     \r\ngifgrep            ?     \r\ngithub             ?     \r\ngog                ?     \r\ngoplaces           ?     \r\nhealthcheck        ?     \r\nhimalaya           ?     \r\nimsg               ?     \r\nmcporter           ?     \r\nmodel-usage        ?     \r\nnano-banana-pro    ?     \r\nnano-pdf           ?     \r\nnotion             ?     \r\nobsidian           ?     \r\nopenai-image-gen   ?     \r\nopenai-whisper     ?     \r\nopenai-whisper-api ?     \r\nopenhue            ?     \r\noracle             ?     \r\nordercli           ?     \r\npeekaboo           ?     \r\nsag                ?     \r\nsession-logs       ?     \r\nsherpa-onnx-tts    ?     \r\nskill-creator      ?     \r\nslack              ?     \r\nsongsee            ?     \r\nsonoscli           ?     \r\nspotify-player     ?     \r\nsummarize          ?     \r\nthings-mac         ?     \r\ntmux               ?     \r\ntrello             ?     \r\nvideo-frames       ?     \r\nvoice-call         ?     \r\nwacli              ?     \r\nweather            ?     \r\nxurl               ?","cwd":"C:\\Users\\14015\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772419271109}}
{"type":"message","id":"103063d5","parentId":"caa98092","timestamp":"2026-03-02T02:41:25.325Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, now I have a complete list of skills. Let me provide a comprehensive answer to the user about:\n1. Midscene.js - what it is\n2. My available tools for UI automation\n3. All my available skills\n\nFrom my system prompt, I have these tools that can do UI automation:\n- browser - Control web browser (click, type, navigate, snapshot, screenshot, etc.)\n- canvas - Present/eval/snapshot the Canvas (for displaying HTML content on nodes)\n- nodes - Control paired nodes (camera/screen/location/notifications)\n\nMidscene.js appears to be a vision-driven UI automation tool for web and mobile apps.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"## 🦐 小虾技能清单 & UI 自动化能力\n\n### 🎯 Midscene.js 是什么？\n**Midscene.js** = 视觉驱动的 UI 自动化框架\n- 支持 Web、iOS、Android\n- 用自然语言控制浏览器和移动应用\n- 跨平台统一 API\n\n---\n\n### 🛠️ 我的 UI 自动化能力\n\n| 工具 | 能力 | 平台 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **browser** | 点击、输入、导航、截图、等待 | Web 浏览器 |\n| **canvas** | 显示 HTML、执行 JS、截图 | 连接的节点 (Mac/iOS/Android) |\n| **nodes** | 屏幕录制、相机、通知控制 | 配对的设备 |\n| **exec** | 执行 PowerShell/命令行 | Windows 宿主机 |\n\n---\n\n### 📚 我所有的技能 (60 个)\n\n**🔧 系统/工具类**\n- `coding-agent` - 委托编码任务给 Codex/Claude Code\n- `healthcheck` - 主机安全加固和审计\n- `skill-creator` - 创建/更新技能包\n- `oracle` - oracle CLI 最佳实践\n\n**📝 笔记/知识类**\n- `apple-notes` / `bear-notes` / `notion` / `obsidian` - 笔记集成\n- `summarize` - 内容摘要\n\n**🎨 媒体/娱乐类**\n- `video-frames` - 视频帧提取 (ffmpeg)\n- `openai-image-gen` - AI 图像生成\n- `gifgrep` - GIF 搜索\n- `songsee` / `spotify-player` / `gog` - 音乐/游戏\n\n**📱 通讯/消息类**\n- `discord` / `slack` / `imsg` / `wacli` - 消息平台\n- `voice-call` - 语音通话\n- `sag` - ElevenLabs TTS 语音合成\n\n**🔍 工具/效率类**\n- `weather` - 天气预报\n- `openai-whisper` - 本地语音转文字\n- `github` / `gh-issues` - GitHub 集成\n- `clawhub` - 技能市场\n- `xurl` - URL 处理\n\n**🍎 Apple 生态**\n- `apple-reminders` / `things-mac` / `sonoscli` / `apple-notes`\n\n**📊 监控/分析**\n- `blogwatcher` - 博客监控\n- `session-logs` - 会话日志\n- `model-usage` - 模型使用统计\n\n**🎮 其他**\n- `camsnap` - 相机快照\n- `canvas` - 画布显示\n- `tmux` - 终端复用\n- `trello` - 项目管理\n- ...等等\n\n---\n\n### 💡 关于\"打开软件/点击\"\n\n**目前我能做的：**\n- ✅ 打开浏览器并访问网页\n- ✅ 在网页上点击、输入、导航\n- ✅ 执行命令行程序\n- ✅ 显示 HTML 内容到 Canvas\n\n**暂时不能做的：**\n- ❌ 直接控制 Windows 桌面应用（如点击 Excel 按钮）\n- ❌ 模拟全局鼠标/键盘事件（需要额外工具如 AutoHotkey）\n\n**如果需要桌面自动化：**\n可以安装 AutoHotkey 或 PyAutoGUI，我帮你写脚本！\n\n---\n\n老板，想用哪个技能？或者需要我帮你安装配置 Midscene.js 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":24263,"output":1064,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25327,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772419271117}}
